Bella!

2161
01:58:01,664 --> 01:58:02,770
Don't move, honey.

2162
01:58:02,906 --> 01:58:05,500
(whimpering)

2163
01:58:05,636 --> 01:58:06,873
(breathing heavily)

2164
01:58:07,008 --> 01:58:09,409
(growling)

2165
